将于12点5分在33号月台开出
<i>Your attention, please. The Miami</i>
<i>Flier departs at 12.05 from 33.</i>

1152
01:27:35,380 --> 01:27:37,371
乘客请尽快上车
<i>All aboard.</i>

1153
01:27:48,626 --> 01:27:52,619
你等一下
Stay right there.
Stay right there.

1154
01:27:52,830 --> 01:27:56,391
你等一下
Stay right there.
Stay right there, honey.

1155
01:28:08,279 --> 01:28:12,147
往迈阿密的特快车
将于12点5分在33号月台开出
<i>Your attention, please.</i>
<i>The Miami Flier, leaving at 12.05,</i>

1156
01:28:12,350 --> 01:28:16,286
请乘客尽快上车
<i>now boarding on track 33.</i>
<i>All aboard!</i>

1157
01:28:29,133 --> 01:28:34,230
就这样停下来
Just here.
I'm just gonna leave this right here.

1158
01:29:22,687 --> 01:29:27,750
请注意,往迈阿密的特快车
<i>Your attention, please.</i>
<i>The Miami Flier, leaving at 12.05,</i>

1159
01:29:27,959 --> 01:29:33,158
将于12点5分在33号月台开出
请乘客尽快上车
<i>is now boarding on track 33.</i>
<i>All aboard!</i>

1160
01:29:33,364 --> 01:29:35,832
再来一次
One more. Here we go.

1161
01:29:57,255 --> 01:30:00,053
来了,准备好吗

1162
01:29:58,315 --> 01:30:00,150
Here we go. You ready?

1163
01:30:01,993 --> 01:30:05,019
我在这里,好吗
I'm right here, honey. Here we go.

1164
01:30:06,940 --> 01:30:10,600
请各位乘客注意
<i>Your attention, please.</i>
<i>May I have your attention, please?</i>

1165
01:30:10,670 --> 01:30:13,002
往迈阿密的特快车最后召集
<i>This is the final call</i>
<i>for the Miami Flier,</i>

1166
01:30:13,490 --> 01:30:18,300
将于12点5分在33号月台开出
请乘客尽快上车
<i>leaving at 12.05 on track 33.</i>
<i>All aboard!</i>

1167
01:30:57,133 --> 01:31:00,261
- 我来帮你
- 真多谢你
- Here, let me. Get your bags.
- Oh, thank you so much. Thank you.

1168
